<%= render 'shared/navbar' %>
<div class="home-container">
  <div class="landing">
    <div class="welcome-card">
      <h2>Welcome to Compassion</h2>
      <br>
      <p>Here you can meet other people and talk about anything you like. You will be connected quickly to anonymous partners who we hope will be able to help you with the struggles of life. Make an account now to get started!</p>
      <br>
      <% unless current_user %>
      <div class="login-signup">
        <%= link_to new_user_session_path do %>
        <button class="button-primary-bordered">Login</button>
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to new_user_registration_path do %>
        <button class="button-secondary-bordered">Signup</button>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="landing-about">
    <div class="about-top">
      <h2>What we offer</h2>
      <p>Mental health issues are becoming more and more widespread. We think our chat and journal features are exactly what people need to feel more supported in what can sometimes be a very lonely world.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-cards">
      <div class="about-card">
        <i class="far fa-comments fa-3x"></i>
        <br>
        <h4>Conversate</h4>
        <p>Our introductory survey will allow us to match you with people we think will be able to best help you in feeling better. Chat with your partners whenever you feel like you need a helping hand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <i class="far fa-comment-alt fa-3x"></i>
        <br>
        <h4>Jump right back in</h4>
        <p>Chats are stored for as long as you choose to keep them active. Pick up right where you left off at any time!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <i class="fas fa-book fa-3x"></i>
        <br>
        <h4>Keep a journal</h4>
        <p>Journalling can be a great way to clarify our thoughts, and to escape certain painful patterns of thinking. You'll have the Compassion journal with you all the time. Accessible through the dashboard.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="landing-questions">
    <div class="question-about">
      <h3>Get the Conversation Going</h3>
      <br>
      <p>Weâ€™ll help you get the chat going by asking three simple conversation starters each day. These answers can serve as the initial premise for building a connection with your partners.</p>
      <%= link_to new_user_registration_path do %>
      <button class="button-primary">Signup</button>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="question-card">
      <span class="question-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-reply fa-lg"></i>
        <i class="far fa-question-circle fa-lg"></i>
      </span>
      <h3>What is your favorite season of the year?</h3>
      <p>Question 3/3</p>
      <%= render 'form' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="homepage-users">
    <div class="home-user-top">
      <h4>Jump right back in where you left off!</h4>
    </div>
    <br><br>
    <div class="home-user-bottom">
      <div class="home-user-cards">
        <i class="fas fa-caret-left fa-5x caret"></i>
        <%= render 'shared/card_ongoing_landing' %>
        <i class="fas fa-caret-right fa-5x caret"></i>
      </div>

    </div>
    <br><br>
